@startuml
title IAB Tech Lab Agentic Advertising - End-to-End Workflow
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Planner as P
participant "Buyer Agent" as BA
participant "Agentic Direct\n(A2A + MCP for OpenDirect)" as AD
participant "Seller Agent" as SA
participant "Agentic Audiences / UCP\n(embeddings)" as UCP

P -> BA : Campaign brief + constraints\n(budget, formats, KPI, dates)

== Audience planning (data plane) ==
BA -> UCP : Build intent representation\n(embedding) + targeting constraints
UCP --> BA : Audience embedding + planning artifacts

== Inventory discovery (control plane) ==
BA -> AD : Discover inventory\n(query / tools)
AD -> SA : OpenDirect list/search\nproducts/avails/pricing
SA --> AD : Candidate products + terms
AD --> BA : Options + terms

== Audience fit / validation (data plane) ==
BA -> UCP : Share audience embedding\nfor validation
UCP -> SA : Exchange embedding\n& policy constraints
SA --> BA : Fit decision\n(accept/reject + guidance)

== Deal creation (control plane) ==
BA -> AD : Request deal\n(create order/line)
AD -> SA : OpenDirect create/confirm\n(negotiate if needed)
SA --> AD : Deal confirmation + Deal ID
AD --> BA : Deal ID for DSP activation

== Post-campaign learning (data plane) ==
SA -> UCP : Reinforcement/response signals\n(outcomes)
UCP --> BA : Feedback for optimization\n(next flight / future planning)

@enduml

